data.description: Immaculately maintained & freshly painted home sitting on an expansive lot. Conveniently set your thermostat on the pellet stove & enjoy the warmth throughout the home. Main level offers tall ceilings & original hardwood floors, bright kitchen with butcher block counters & farm sink, 3 bedrooms, a full bath & utility room.Upstairs will bring you to an oversized bedroom, bonus room & half bath. Storm windows for all windows!Mudroom provides storage space w/access to the back deck.Detached 2 car garage/shop with power. Fruit trees(pear, fig, apple & cherries + grapes).Located across the street from Raymond School & walking distance to parks!Conventionally located along the coast between Seattle & Portland and just a short drive to the Ocean!
